Hablamemo
----------

Description
-----------
Increase your memory skills while learning a new language. Create a vocabulary kvtml file (e.g. in Parley), load it to Hablamemo, select your level and you are ready! Image mode is also supported. Hablamemo widgets comes with a sample of spanish-english and spanish-greek vocabulary files. You are stronly encouraged to use your own vocabulary files.

//TODO: Reference to GCompris


Dependencies
------------
- Plasma 5.0 or later

- Qt 5 xmllistmodel QML module (In Debian/Ubuntu, install: qml-module-qtquick-xmllistmodel)


Installation
------------
- Add Widgets... -> Get new widgets -> Download new plasma widgets


